                            ----------------------
                            Who is Epic MegaGames?
                            ----------------------

Epic MegaGames is a world leader in developing and publishing shareware
games.  Epic's top hits include Epic Pinball, Jazz Jackrabbit, One Must Fall
2097, and the classic Jill of the Jungle.  More top-quality games
such as New Order and Jazz 2 are coming soon - so stay tuned!

Epic is based in Rockville, Maryland.  The Epic team includes 15 employees 
and more than 30 independent programmers, artists, and musicians.  Everybody 
at Epic is dedicated to bringing you great shareware games.


